    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.25.2-3_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">2</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        King Edward VI High School for girls,
                        Edgbaston Park Road,
                        Edgbaston
                        Birmingham, 15
                        6th January, 1957.
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Mr. Neihardt,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I hope you do not mind my writing to you, and that you can find time to answer me. I have just read your book "Eagle Voice" so I think that you could tell me what I want to know.</p>
                
                <p>Is there such a place as Pine Ridge Reservation and if so where is it? If not do you know of another Ogalalla Indian Reservation and where it is?</p>
                
                <p>I should be very grateful if you could answer my letter as I do not know of anyone else to ask and the information will be valuable to me.</p>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.25.2-3_0002"/>
                
                    <fw type="authorial">II</fw>
                
                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours Sincerely</salute>
                    <signed>Kathryn Tongue</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="curatorial"><hi rend="caps">JOHN G. NEIHARDT CENTER</hi></note>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.25.2-3_0003"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">3</fw>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    BIRMINGHAM 7-PM 5 JAN 1957 A
                
                    HAVE Y<unclear reason="missing"/>
                    TAKEN<unclear reason="missing"/>
                    YOUR L<unclear reason="missing"/>
                    FOR RA<unclear reason="missing"/>
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Mr. <hi rend="caps">J. G.</hi> Neihardt,</addrLine>
                            <addrLine>University of Missouri,</addrLine>
                                <addrLine>Columbia,</addrLine>
                                    <addrLine>Missouri,</addrLine>
                                        <addrLine><hi rend="caps">U.S.A.</hi></addrLine>
                    </address>
                </ab>
                
            </div1>
